Who'd believe that?

261
00:16:43,110 --> 00:16:47,180
You killed Kim Myung Hui
and kept Kim Dan Hui by your side.

262
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:49,180
The details are just too shocking.

263
00:16:49,810 --> 00:16:51,780
This isn't going to be an easy fix.

264
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:55,520
Stay out of it and leave.

265
00:16:56,050 --> 00:16:59,260
Actually, I have every right
to be involved.

266
00:17:00,020 --> 00:17:03,390
I'm also a victim whom you deceived
and made a fool of for 30 years.

267
00:17:04,530 --> 00:17:07,260
What? A victim?

268
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:08,570
That's right.

269
00:17:08,630 --> 00:17:12,040
You killed Kim Myung Hui
and framed me for it.

270
00:17:12,370 --> 00:17:15,010
You made me spend 30 years
fighting with Kim Dan Hui.

271
00:17:15,070 --> 00:17:16,410
So what?

272
00:17:17,210 --> 00:17:19,540
Should I lock you in the basement
like I did with Kim Dan Hui?

273
00:17:21,910 --> 00:17:23,580
Do you still not understand
the situation?

274
00:17:24,820 --> 00:17:28,620
What if I side with Kim Dan Hui
and testify that you're a murderer,

275
00:17:29,020 --> 00:17:33,160
and that I saw everything go down
30 years ago?

276
00:17:34,730 --> 00:17:36,990
- What?
- On the other hand,

277
00:17:37,630 --> 00:17:41,330
if I testify that
Kim Dan Hui is lying,

278
00:17:41,670 --> 00:17:42,730
what's in it for me?

279
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:49,310
Which side I take and what I say...

280
00:17:50,110 --> 00:17:51,540
is entirely up to you.

281
00:17:53,380 --> 00:17:55,650
So you'd better get on my good side.

282
00:17:55,710 --> 00:17:57,410
Over my dead body.

283
00:18:01,490 --> 00:18:02,890
Sir.

284
00:18:04,120 --> 00:18:05,290
Now what?

285
00:18:05,290 --> 00:18:07,260
An emergency board meeting
was called...

286
00:18:07,590 --> 00:18:11,060
- regarding your removal.
- His removal?

287
00:18:11,330 --> 00:18:13,630
Who would dare to do that?

288
00:18:13,860 --> 00:18:15,830
Director Park Min Jun called for it.

289
00:18:17,170 --> 00:18:18,470
Min Jun?

290
00:18:19,770 --> 00:18:22,110
Cancel the board meeting right now.

291
00:18:22,570 --> 00:18:25,380
Well, according to the bylaws,
an emergency meeting...

292
00:18:26,380 --> 00:18:28,680
can only be canceled
by the person who called it,

293
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:30,210
unless the issue is resolved.

294
00:18:31,780 --> 00:18:33,080
Park Min Jun.

295
00:18:33,920 --> 00:18:36,250
Find him and bring him to me now.

296
00:18:36,320 --> 00:18:38,760
I have to cancel
the emergency board meeting!

297
00:18:38,890 --> 00:18:42,030
And what if you can't?
You need to think very carefully.

298
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:44,500
If it looks like you're going
to lose your chairmanship...

299
00:18:44,500 --> 00:18:46,160
to Kim Dan Hui and Park Min Jun,

300
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:47,630
give it to Hyun Jun.

301
00:18:48,430 --> 00:18:50,430
Who'd take it from me?

302
00:18:50,430 --> 00:18:52,840
- Go to the office now.
- Yes, sir.

303
00:19:07,580 --> 00:19:09,820
Man, this is a real rollercoaster.

304
00:19:10,020 --> 00:19:12,020
First Chairman Park's recording,
now an emergency board meeting.

305
00:19:12,090 --> 00:19:14,090
It's making my head spin.

306
00:19:14,790 --> 00:19:17,590
Of course Kim Dan Hui
wouldn't come back without a plan.

307
00:19:18,300 --> 00:19:20,360
She planned all of this
from the start.

308
00:19:20,560 --> 00:19:22,670
So what should we do?

309
00:19:23,300 --> 00:19:24,300
Ms. Oh.

310
00:19:26,600 --> 00:19:28,910
- The chairman's recording...
- I know.

311
00:19:29,210 --> 00:19:30,710
It's true, so drop it.

312
00:19:30,710 --> 00:19:32,980
What about
the emergency board meeting?

313
00:19:33,310 --> 00:19:35,310
Shouldn't we stop his removal?

314
00:19:39,180 --> 00:19:42,150
This is a no-brainer.
If the chairman is removed,

315
00:19:42,150 --> 00:19:44,120
the other side will take over
the entire company.

316
00:19:44,690 --> 00:19:46,160
It's to our advantage
to stop the removal first,

317
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:47,790
and then demand compensation.

318
00:19:48,360 --> 00:19:49,360
Right.

319
00:19:50,790 --> 00:19:51,860
I may hate Park Tae Ho,

320
00:19:51,930 --> 00:19:53,630
but I can't let them
take the company.

321
00:19:55,230 --> 00:19:56,930
Just like you said,
we'll block the dismissal...

322
00:19:56,930 --> 00:19:58,400
and demand compensation.

323
00:19:58,900 --> 00:20:01,640
I need to get Director Seo
and our directors in line first.

324
00:20:02,040 --> 00:20:04,540
You go to the company
and see what's going on.

325
00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:06,310
Got it.

326
00:20:15,320 --> 00:20:16,650
The chairman is here.

327
00:20:17,290 --> 00:20:18,790
Is the recording true?

328
00:20:18,860 --> 00:20:21,260
Is it true that you murdered
the woman carrying your son?

329
00:20:21,330 --> 00:20:22,860
Where is Kim Dan Hui now?

330
00:20:23,860 --> 00:20:25,860
Everyone,

331
00:20:26,430 --> 00:20:29,400
it's all lies. Lies!

332
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:31,570
- Let's get you to your office.
- Chairman,

333
00:20:31,570 --> 00:20:33,240
is it true you murdered her?

334
00:20:35,570 --> 00:20:36,770
Hey, Manager Kang.

335
00:20:37,370 --> 00:20:39,310
Park Min Jun is on the second floor.
Go get him.

336
00:20:39,980 --> 00:20:44,550
Excuse me, sir.
Is the recording true? Sir!

337
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:47,580
The recording was released,
and he's still calling it a lie.

338
00:20:48,290 --> 00:20:51,790
He'll use the power of Adele Group
to try and cover it up.

339
00:20:52,660 --> 00:20:55,430
We have to get him dismissed
at the board meeting today.

340
00:20:59,200 --> 00:21:01,160
I also got the test results back.

341
00:21:01,770 --> 00:21:05,070
If we can prove Chairman Park
committed murder, we can win.

342
00:21:05,140 --> 00:21:08,270
After my father is dismissed,
what's the plan?

343
00:21:08,370 --> 00:21:09,570
Like last time,

344
00:21:10,110 --> 00:21:12,110
do you still think my mother
should become the chairwoman?

345
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:16,150
To make sure Park Tae Ho
and Oh Jung Ran are punished,

346
00:21:16,750 --> 00:21:19,550
it's probably best for your mother
to have the power.

347
00:21:25,760 --> 00:21:27,560
(Park Hyun Jun)

348
00:21:30,690 --> 00:21:32,560
We should tell Hyun Jun now, too.

349
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:35,530
Things are moving
too fast right now.

350
00:21:36,530 --> 00:21:39,870
It's better to explain everything
after this is all over.

351
00:21:40,700 --> 00:21:44,570
Are we going to keep hiding the fact
that we know his secret?

352
00:21:45,110 --> 00:21:46,110
Yes.

353
00:21:46,210 --> 00:21:48,280
I'm going to let his secret rest
for now.

354
00:21:49,310 --> 00:21:51,480
Let's prepare
for the board meeting first.

355
00:22:18,080 --> 00:22:19,810
(Head of Division 2, Park Hyun Jun)

356
00:22:21,650 --> 00:22:23,950
They knew my secret all along.

357
00:22:25,650 --> 00:22:27,980
Park Min Jun and Baek Jin Ju.

358
00:22:30,520 --> 00:22:33,490
They know I'm not Park Tae Ho's son.

359
00:22:35,160 --> 00:22:36,160
That's why...

360
00:22:47,100 --> 00:22:49,470
That's why she chose them over me.

361
00:22:51,680 --> 00:22:53,040
She abandoned me...

362
00:22:54,640 --> 00:22:57,410
for Park Min Jun,
the son of Park Tae Ho.

363
00:23:01,950 --> 00:23:03,220
Darn it!

364
00:23:19,770 --> 00:23:21,270
The chairman is looking for you.

365
00:23:21,810 --> 00:23:25,580
- Please come with me.
- No, I'm going to the boardroom.

366
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:32,180
Jin Ju, you go on ahead.

367
00:23:56,070 --> 00:23:57,070
Park Hyun Jun.

368
00:23:57,470 --> 00:23:58,610
How long have you known?

369
00:23:59,640 --> 00:24:01,240
What are you talking about
all of a sudden?

370
00:24:01,610 --> 00:24:04,680
How and when did you find out
who my father is?

371
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:09,920
I knew it.

372
00:24:11,620 --> 00:24:13,990
So that's why you lied to me,
kept secrets,

373
00:24:14,830 --> 00:24:17,190
and sided with President Kim
and Park Min Jun.

374
00:24:17,860 --> 00:24:19,760
Because I'm not Park Tae Ho's son.

375
00:24:20,460 --> 00:24:22,470
Because I'm useless to you now!

376
00:24:23,970 --> 00:24:25,100
That's not it.

377
00:24:25,700 --> 00:24:27,370
This has nothing to do with you.

378
00:24:27,370 --> 00:24:28,470
Exactly!

379
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:32,210
I'm just some guy
you couldn't care less about, right?

380
00:24:34,080 --> 00:24:35,680
The son of a chauffeur.

381
00:24:37,950 --> 00:24:40,520
Someone you can just throw away
when he's no longer useful.

382
00:24:41,120 --> 00:24:42,190
Park Hyun Jun.

383
00:24:43,290 --> 00:24:44,350
I...

384
00:24:49,260 --> 00:24:50,360
What are you doing?

385
00:24:50,960 --> 00:24:54,230
I can't just be a fool
who gets thrown away by you.

386
00:24:55,670 --> 00:24:57,330
The son of Chairman Park Tae Ho.

387
00:24:58,740 --> 00:25:00,240
I have to at least hold on
to that position.

388
00:25:03,510 --> 00:25:04,510
Park Hyun Jun.

389
00:25:21,220 --> 00:25:24,590
Without proof, it'll be hard
to persuade the directors.

390
00:25:26,430 --> 00:25:29,930
Before the board meeting starts,
I have to get the test results back.

391
00:25:32,870 --> 00:25:35,910
But what if
I can't get there in time?

392
00:25:48,390 --> 00:25:49,490
It's me, Secretary Jung.

393
00:25:50,150 --> 00:25:51,320
There's a problem.

394
00:25:52,390 --> 00:25:54,490
You need to rescue
Ms. Kim right now...

395
00:25:54,560 --> 00:25:56,090
and bring her to the boardroom.

396
00:25:58,130 --> 00:26:01,500
She needs to be the one
to personally expose Park Tae Ho...

397
00:26:02,100 --> 00:26:03,530
as a murderer.

398
00:26:35,770 --> 00:26:39,500
Cancel the emergency board meeting
right now.

399
00:26:39,770 --> 00:26:41,440
No. You're...

400
00:26:42,140 --> 00:26:43,170
a murderer.

401
00:26:43,710 --> 00:26:45,610
You shouldn't be
in the chairman's seat.

402
00:26:46,810 --> 00:26:48,750
Me? A murderer?

403
00:26:52,380 --> 00:26:55,190
I'm your father.
You're Park Tae Ho's son.

404
00:26:55,790 --> 00:26:56,790
Your mother...

405
00:26:57,620 --> 00:26:59,160
Well, actually,

406
00:26:59,890 --> 00:27:03,090
she isn't even your mother.
So just betray her.

407
00:27:03,990 --> 00:27:07,700
Stop being so emotional
and think rationally.

408
00:27:09,200 --> 00:27:12,070
Think about which side is going
to benefit you more,

409
00:27:13,070 --> 00:27:14,070
and open your eyes.

410
00:27:14,700 --> 00:27:18,440
I get it. Was murder
one of your rational calculations?

411
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:22,180
Did you decide
it was more beneficial...

412
00:27:22,250 --> 00:27:24,810
to just kill the woman
carrying your unborn child?

413
00:27:26,450 --> 00:27:29,450
Was that actually rational
on your part?

414
00:27:30,220 --> 00:27:32,990
- You brat.
- Park Tae Ho, you...

415
00:27:34,060 --> 00:27:38,330
killed my birth mother
and ruined both of our lives.

416
00:27:38,700 --> 00:27:43,600
You killed the innocent CEO Baek,
and you took Jin Ju away from me.

417
00:27:44,900 --> 00:27:47,870
Now it's your turn to be ruined,

418
00:27:47,940 --> 00:27:51,310
and to know the pain of having
everything taken from you.

419
00:27:52,480 --> 00:27:53,480
You little punk.

420
00:28:03,620 --> 00:28:06,460
How dare you speak to me like that?

421
00:28:07,490 --> 00:28:09,130
Both your mother and Baek Jun Gi...

422
00:28:09,760 --> 00:28:13,630
died because they dared to defy me.

423
00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:20,300
You and Kim Dan Hui lived in luxury
under my protection.

424
00:28:20,900 --> 00:28:22,210
And now this?

425
00:28:26,180 --> 00:28:28,980
Do you really think
you can take me down?

426
00:28:29,910 --> 00:28:31,650
I am the Adele Group,

427
00:28:32,820 --> 00:28:35,620
and the Adele Group is me.

428
00:28:40,760 --> 00:28:42,390
I wouldn't be so sure about that.

429
00:28:44,130 --> 00:28:45,130
Hyun Jun.

430
00:28:45,130 --> 00:28:48,260
The board is deadlocked
regarding your removal.

431
00:28:49,230 --> 00:28:51,630
If concrete evidence
of the murder is revealed,

432
00:28:52,600 --> 00:28:53,740
you'll be ousted.

433
00:28:54,840 --> 00:28:56,440
Concrete evidence?

434
00:28:57,010 --> 00:28:59,680
The evidence that Park Min Jun
and Chloe prepared together.

435
00:29:01,780 --> 00:29:02,950
It's in my hands now.

436
00:29:05,420 --> 00:29:07,280
Chloe too?

437
00:29:07,950 --> 00:29:08,950
I knew it.

438
00:29:09,450 --> 00:29:11,550
Kim Dan Hui and Chloe.

439
00:29:13,760 --> 00:29:15,530
They plotted this together?

440
00:29:15,860 --> 00:29:18,530
Park Hyun Jun,
what do you think you're doing?

441
00:29:31,810 --> 00:29:33,180
I helped you, Father.

442
00:29:34,980 --> 00:29:38,150
More than Min Jun,
I'm the one who deserves...

443
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:40,820
to be your son.

444
00:29:42,250 --> 00:29:43,250
Park Hyun Jun.

445
00:29:58,230 --> 00:30:01,800
I have to rescue Dan Hui
and get her to the board meeting.

446
00:30:02,410 --> 00:30:04,410
Yes. This should do the trick.

447
00:30:07,180 --> 00:30:09,480
Nothing beats this
for breaking down a door.

448
00:30:10,410 --> 00:30:13,020
Wait, how would you know that?

449
00:30:14,150 --> 00:30:15,850
When you work a lot
of part-time jobs,

450
00:30:15,850 --> 00:30:18,960
you see things you wouldn't believe.

451
00:30:25,160 --> 00:30:26,160
Nice.

452
00:30:27,530 --> 00:30:28,530
I'll get going.

453
00:30:29,600 --> 00:30:30,770
Be careful.

454
00:30:39,510 --> 00:30:41,080
Dan Hui.

455
00:30:41,480 --> 00:30:43,610
- Dan Hui!
- Hold it.

456
00:30:50,950 --> 00:30:52,560
I knew it.

457
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:56,390
Kim Dan Hui isn't going
to the board meeting.

458
00:31:08,070 --> 00:31:10,370
I'm telling you,
the recording was fabricated.

459
00:31:11,810 --> 00:31:14,280
Don't you know how sophisticated
AI technology is these days?

460
00:31:14,710 --> 00:31:16,180
We can ask the police
to investigate...

461
00:31:17,180 --> 00:31:20,150
and find the person
who spread this fake recording.

462
00:31:20,420 --> 00:31:23,320
So is the recording
really a fabrication?

463
00:31:23,890 --> 00:31:24,890
That's what I said!

464
00:31:24,950 --> 00:31:28,290
Don't we need to hear from Ms. Kim,
instead of only hearing from you?

465
00:31:31,590 --> 00:31:33,030
Well, that's...

466
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:46,340
The recording wasn't fabricated.
It's completely real.

467
00:31:47,140 --> 00:31:48,140
Park Tae Ho...

468
00:31:49,150 --> 00:31:52,120
is the man who murdered my sister.

469
00:32:37,830 --> 00:32:40,630
(Pearl in Red)

470
00:32:41,700 --> 00:32:43,100
What is this nonsense?

471
00:32:43,230 --> 00:32:44,800
Who dares to try and take me down?

472
00:32:45,030 --> 00:32:48,600
I am the Adele Group,
and the Adele Group is me.

473
00:32:48,710 --> 00:32:51,670
Things are about to get
a lot harder for you.

474
00:32:51,870 --> 00:32:54,610
You'll regret the day
you betrayed me,

475
00:32:54,610 --> 00:32:58,480
and all the wrong you've done
will come back to destroy you.

476
00:32:58,750 --> 00:33:00,280
I can't go down like this.

477
00:33:00,520 --> 00:33:01,580
I have to survive somehow,

478
00:33:01,580 --> 00:33:03,620
even if it means clinging
to the chairman or Hyun Jun.

479
00:33:04,050 --> 00:33:06,260
- A solution?
- Back me to take your place.

480
00:33:06,490 --> 00:33:08,320
I'll step up as the next chairman.

481
00:33:09,690 --> 00:33:11,360
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
